commit.message: Add initial tests for trivial SquashFS images
Add a script to generate test cases
Fix incorrect conditional around LZ4 block.

Test patch input for patch format.

This makes it possible to extend the tool with support for more patch
formats in the future.

Make thread_no an unsigned int.

To avoid comparison between signed & unsigned.

Run last of the concurrent jobs in main thread.

There is no point spawning N threads and keeping main thread idle.
Instead, spawn N-1 threads and run the last job in main thread.
Use pthread to compress multiple blocks simultaneously.

Read compression info from patch header.

As a result, squashmerge is no longer SquashFS-aware.
Iterate over blocks in target file and truncate it.
Move input expansion into separate function.
Create the expanded output file using delta.
